(Plot Details) Jessica moves into Coldhill Estates looking to make a fresh start after a messy divorce. But the seemingly peaceful apartment complex hidden in the woods is home to a slew of horror stories and nightmares. Ghost, werewolves, and the wrath of hell await you...welcome to Coldhill...enjoy your stay.
